ef="https://www.tmz.com/2023/07/15/alex-volkanovski-says-zuckerberg-serious-fighting-elon-musk-mma-ufc/">综合格斗传奇人物亚历克斯·沃尔卡诺夫斯基 (Alex Volkanovsky) 表示，扎克似乎已经准备好接受挑战。</a>尽管马斯克通常将整件事当作一个笑话，但马斯克确实为这场战斗做好了准备，他接受了 UFC 冠军乔治·圣皮埃尔的训练邀请，并<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/lexfridman/status/1673836162937417728">与播客莱克斯·弗里德曼进行了对打。</a>当然，那时他会暂时停止转发（重新转发？） <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.businessinsider.com/elon-musk-shares-anti-trans-content-twitter-2023-6">可恶的反跨性别内容</a>，并更改网站规则以<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-quietly-reversed-its-policies-to-allow-for-intentional-deadnaming-and-misgendering-181754382.html">允许性别歧视。</a> UFC主席达纳怀特也告诉记者，该组织已准备好协助此次活动。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/looks-like-the-zuck-vs-musk-fight-isnt-happening-195538503.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/looks-like-the-zuck-vs-musk-fight-isnt-happening-195538503.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ff9e49ac-706a-4ef9-a492-27030c36c274</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jul 2023 19:55:38 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690577785</ingested><modified> 2023-07-28T20:56:29+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Martial Arts]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1177" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/e2cae550-2d77-11ee-afbf-a95d2b7237e8" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><med