<h2> <strong>Powerbeats Pro</strong> </h2><p><core-commerce id="63b4fdb8ac67421a8c8f5591cc156c95" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>在<a data-i13n="cpos:85;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-workout-headphones-191517835.html">我们的健身耳机指南</a>中，我们将<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Target;elmt:;cpos:84;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=827d7835-78d6-4491-ae04-c042cab1d6e7&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Target&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4MjdkNzgzNS03OGQ2LTQ0OTEtYWUwNC1jMDQyY2FiMWQ2ZTciLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGFyZ2V0LmNvbS9wL3Bvd2VyYmVhdHMtcHJvLXRydWUtd2lyZWxlc3MtYmx1ZXRvb3RoLWVhcnBob25lcy8tL0EtNzgzNjIwMzU_cHJlc2VsZWN0PTU0NjEwODk4IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJhM2ExN2Y0Yi0yOTMxLTQ1YTktOTdlMi1lYTUxZWIyODNmYjEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAU8P70mM4Zrtg-gjdQ38m5oLl0ObGcCUqD6RMtpGTr3v&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fpowerbeats-pro-true-wireless-bluetooth-earphones%2F-%2FA-78362035%3Fpreselect%3D54610898" class="rapid-with-clickid">Powerbeats Pro</a>称为最舒适的选择。控件很直观，iOS 集成很棒，舒适的耳后挂钩很容易固定到位并保持不动（尽管它们可能会干扰太阳镜）。当它们在 2019 年推出时，我们给它们的<a data-i13n="cpos:86;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-05-16-beats-powerbeats-pro-review.html">Engadget 评分为 86 分。</a>它们现在有点老了，包耳式设计并不能阻挡任何噪音，但它们目前比建议零售价低 90 美元，大约是比他们最近的售价便宜 40 美元，与亚马逊 Prime Day 促销价一致。</p><h2><strong>顶空</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="1ad719f660024091a0c1d87281a7782d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:88;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gifts-for-teachers-130002962.html">指南</a>中多次推荐<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Headspace;elmt:;cpos:87;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e3494264-16cf-476b-92a8-2dfe2c12bfa0&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Headspace&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiO